name: AstroBabes
description:

https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi - commissions open!
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

AstroBabes

LET US GO TO THE STARS,
WHERE NOBODY KNOWS WHO WE ARE

LET US FLY, FAR AWAY
TO THE ENDS OF THE MILKY WAY!

I HAVE SEEN, AND I HAVE LOVED
BUT THERE WAS NEVER SOMEONE LIKE YOU
I HAVE BEEN MISINFORMED
THEY TOLD ME I COULD NOT BE WITH YOU

ASTROBABE, YOU'RE MY ASTROBABE
I WILL ALWAYS KEEP YOU CLOSE
ASTROBABE, OH MY ASTROBABE
I WILL HOLD ONTO THIS CHOICE

ASTROBABE, YOU'RE MY ASTROBABE
TOGETHER, OH! WE FLY SO HIGH!
ASTROBABE, OH MY ASTROBABE
TONIGHT, FAR AWAY WE FLYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY!

guitar solo

DESCRIPTION:

This LoRA is an opportunity to give a mad shout of to Mister @fking
You HAVE TO check his work, mainly his fking_scifi_v2 SD 2.1 model for which I intend to retrain and release another AstroBabe LoRA.
Please do not overlook his work!

And now,

Go download this LoRA and get your AstroBabe!
